<br>
It's amazing how everyone wants a manaburning wizard around when it suits their purpose.  If I get asked to go help someone get their scale from Serv in the chat channel what do I see spammed from half the raid? &quot;How many wizards do we have on the raid, do they all have MB?&quot;  Then the tells come in, &quot;Do you have MB?&quot;<br>
<br>
If I go on any big named raid someone always asks, &quot;Do we have any MB'ing wizards?&quot; <br>
<br>
On a weekly, if not daily, basis I now get asked by random_n00b_01, &quot;Do you have MB, and if so could you come help me out with my epic piece in &lt;insert zone here&gt;&quot;  Yes, I used to get asked before, but not as frequently and now it ALWAYS starts out with, &quot;Do you have manaburn?&quot;<br>
<br>
I'm just so sick and tired of all the whining, the bitching, the crying that comes associated with this class and skill now.  Before we got it all you heard were wizards doing the bitching and crying about how we weren't balanced enough.  Now it's the entire freaking server.  On boards, in guild, in chat channels, crying about how we're over powered because we can kill old world mobs when we put our resources together!<br>
<br>
I don't go saying chanters should be nerfed because they can go solo the Kael arena, or because druids can go solo wolves (or the gimpier dragons) in WW and sell the furs for profit.  I say, &quot;Hell yeah, good for you!  That is so cool!  I'm a bit jealous!  Mind if I tag along?&quot;<br>
<br>
I'm not much into the manaburn crew on brell.  In fact, the only thing I look forward to taking out with a huge crew of my fellow wizards are things like Sonty, the bigger boys that take more of a combined effort.  Because, it will be a hell of a lot of fun to go and try. <br>
<br>
Yep, sucks if a group of them want to get together to take out a mob like VS that someone is trying to get for their epic.  But, that's life.  People will do strange things, mean things, bad things, good things, whatever throughout eq with manaburn or not.<br>
<br>
So please people, stop the bitching.  I know that this post really has nothing to do with the original post it's just that I've had it with all the moaning.  You can bitch when you stop sending me tells to find out if I have manaburn to serve your purpose.<br>
<br>
Ankhamun of the Nexus<br>
Poison Arrow<br>
